{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1228204, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 242218, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "2", "timestamp": 1615303127, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1228222, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 242218, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1246", "timestamp": 1615303213, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1228224, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 242218, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "235", "timestamp": 1615303257, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1228261, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 242218, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "出处：Maslach, C., & Leiter, M. P. (2008). The truth about burnout: How organizations cause personal stress and what to do about it. John Wiley & Sons.\n当然，洞主看的不是原文，而是这个总结版：\nhttps://www.forbes.com/sites/johnrampton/2015/05/13/the-6-causes-of-professional-burnout-and-how-to-avoid-them/?sh=51d789211dde", "timestamp": 1615303469, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1228264, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 242218, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我自己的话，136吧", "timestamp": 1615303488, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1228409, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 242218, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "3", "timestamp": 1615304386, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1228530, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 242218, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "16", "timestamp": 1615305257, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 14, "pid": 242218, "reply": 7, "tag": null, "text": "Burnout的六种可能的原因：\n1. Lack of control: 对过程或结果缺少控制感（换言之，过多的不确定性）\n2. Insufficient reward: 回报与预期不对等，包括物质的、社会的和价值的回报\n3. Lack of community: 缺少归属感与社会支持\n4. Absence of fairness: 不公平感\n5. Conflict in values: 任务与自己价值观的冲突\n6. Work overload: 过大的任务量或者过高的任务难度\n大部分时候，我们都以为是因为第六条才觉得身心俱疲，其实前五条也可能是重要原因。\n欢迎对号入座", "timestamp": 1615303044, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1615305255, "url": "", "vote": {}}}